			<div class="dablink">For the World War II German offensive, see <a href="/wiki/Crimean_Campaign_(1941%E2%80%931942)" title="Crimean Campaign (1941–1942)">Crimean Campaign (1941–1942)</a>.  For the World War II Soviet offensive, see <a href="/wiki/Crimean_Offensive_(1944)" title="Crimean Offensive (1944)">Crimean Offensive (1944)</a>.</div>
