</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:Malakhov1.jpg" class="image" title="Malakhov1.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/31/Malakhov1.jpg/300px-Malakhov1.jpg" width="300" height="224" border="0" /></a><br />
Detail of <a href="/wiki/Franz_Roubaud" title="Franz Roubaud">Franz Roubaud</a>'s <a href="/wiki/Panoramic_painting" title="Panoramic painting">panoramic painting</a> <i>The Siege of Sevastopol</i> (1904).</td>
</tr>
