<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFMoon2001">Moon, David (2001). <i>The Abolition of Serfdom in Russia, 1762-1907</i>. Harlow, England: Pearson Education. pp.&#160;49–55. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/058229486X" class="internal">ISBN 058229486X</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Abolition+of+Serfdom+in+Russia%2C+1762-1907&amp;rft.aulast=Moon&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft.au=Moon%2C+David&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B49%E2%80%9355&amp;rft.place=Harlow%2C+England&amp;rft.pub=Pearson+Education&amp;rft.isbn=058229486X&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Crimean_War"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
