<li>Russell, William Howard, "The Crimean War: As Seen by Those Who Reported It". Baton Rouge LA.&#160;:<a href="/wiki/Louisiana_State_University_Press" title="Louisiana State University Press">Louisiana State University Press</a>, 2009 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780807134450" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-8071-3445-0</a></li>
